#: C/software-metadata.page:130
msgid "Age rating"
msgstr "Vekové hodnotenie"

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:131
msgid ""
"<app>Software</app> displays an age rating tile on the details page for an application. This "
"shows what age range the application should be suitable for, based on different kinds of content "
