#. (itstool) path: section/title
#: C/software-metadata.page:292
msgid "How to add missing content rating information"
msgstr "Ako pridať chýbajúce informácie o hodnotení obsahu"

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:293
msgid ""
"The content rating information for an application is stored in the <link href=\"https://"
"www.freedesktop.org/software/appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-"
"content_rating\"><code>&lt;content_rating&gt;</code></link> element within the application’s "
"<code>&lt;component&gt;</code> in its metainfo file."
msgstr ""
"Informácie o hodnotení obsahu pre aplikáciu sú uložené v prvku <link href=\"https://"
"www.freedesktop.org/software/appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-"
"content_rating\"><code>&lt;content_rating&gt;</code></link> v rámci <code>&lt;component&gt;</"
"code> aplikácie v jej súbore metainfo."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:294
msgid ""
"Applications should use the OARS 1.1 standard to fill in this element. If the "
"<code>&lt;content_rating&gt;</code> element is not specified, the application’s content rating "
"is unknown. If it’s specified but empty, the application has no content which might be "
"unsuitable for any audience."
msgstr ""
"Aplikácie by mali použiť štandard OARS 1.1 na vyplnenie tohto prvku. Ak nie je špecifikovaný "
"prvok <code>&lt;content_rating&gt;</code>, hodnotenie obsahu aplikácie je neznáme. Ak je "
"špecifikované, ale prázdne, aplikácia nemá žiadny obsah, ktorý by mohol byť nevhodný pre "
"akúkoľvek cieľovú skupinu."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:295
msgid ""
"Use <link href=\"https://hughsie.github.io/oars/\">the OARS generator</link> to produce suitable "
"content rating information for an application."
msgstr ""
"Použite <link href=\"https://hughsie.github.io/oars/\">generátor OARS</link> na vytvorenie "
"vhodných informácií o hodnotení obsahu pre aplikáciu."

#. (itstool) path: section/title
#: C/software-metadata.page:299
msgid "How to fix incorrect licensing information"
msgstr "Ako opraviť nesprávne informácie o licenciách"

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:300
msgid ""
"The licensing information for an application is stored in the <link href=\"https://"
"www.freedesktop.org/software/appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-"
"project_license\"><code>&lt;project_license&gt;</code></link> element within the application’s "
"<code>&lt;component&gt;</code> in its metainfo file."
msgstr ""
"Informácie o licenciách pre aplikáciu sú uložené v prvku <link href=\"https://"
"www.freedesktop.org/software/appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-"
"project_license\"><code>&lt;project_license&gt;</code></link> v rámci <code>&lt;component&gt;</"
"code> aplikácie v jej súbore metainfo."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:301
msgid ""
"The content in this element should be an <link href=\"https://spdx.org/specifications\">SPDX "
"expression</link> which describes the ‘main’ license for the project. This should typically be "
"the license of the code, and not include the license of the documentation or ancillary content."
msgstr ""
"Obsah tohto prvku by malo byť <link href=\"https://spdx.org/specifications\">výrazom SPDX</link>, "
"ktorý opisuje „hlavnú“ licenciu projektu. Toto by typicky mal byť licenciou kódu a nemalo by "
"zahŕňať licenciu dokumentácie alebo vedľajšieho obsahu."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:302
msgid ""
"If the SPDX expression is a single license, or an ‘or’ combination of multiple licenses, which "
"are all <link href=\"https://spdx.org/licenses/\">FSF or OSI approved</link>, the application is "
"considered ‘free software’ and the license tile says so. Otherwise, it’s considered "
"‘proprietary’."
msgstr ""
"Ak je výraz SPDX jednou licenciou alebo kombináciou viacerých licencií „alebo“, ktoré sú všetky "
"<link href=\"https://spdx.org/licenses/\">schválené FSF alebo OSI</link>, aplikácia sa považuje "
"za „slobodný softvér“ a dlaždica licencie to hovorí. Inak sa považuje za „proprietárny“."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:303
msgid ""
"If an application is being displayed as ‘proprietary’ when you think it shouldn’t be, it’s "
"likely that the <code>&lt;project_license&gt;</code> element includes the documentation license "
"for the project. Remove it."
msgstr ""
"Ak sa aplikácia zobrazuje ako „proprietárna“, keď si myslíte, že by nemala byť, je pravdepodobné, "
"že prvok <code>&lt;project_license&gt;</code> zahŕňa licenciu dokumentácie projektu. Odstráňte "
"ju."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:304
msgid ""
"<link href=\"https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/meld/-/issues/579\">For example</link>, change the "
"license metadata from:"
msgstr ""
"<link href=\"https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/meld/-/issues/579\">Napríklad</link> zmeňte metadáta "
"licencie z:"

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:306
msgid "to"
msgstr "na"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:311
msgid ""
"<link href=\"https://tecnocode.co.uk/2021/07/05/dont-generally-put-cc-by-sa-in-appdata/\">Don’t "
"(generally) put documentation license in appdata</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link href=\"https://tecnocode.co.uk/2021/07/05/dont-generally-put-cc-by-sa-in-appdata/"
"\">Neumiestňujte (všeobecne) licenciu dokumentácie do appdata</link>"

#. (itstool) path: section/title
#: C/software-metadata.page:320
msgid "How to add missing links"
msgstr "Ako pridať chýbajúce odkazy"

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:321
msgid ""
"The links for an application are stored as <link href=\"https://www.freedesktop.org/software/"
"appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-url\"><code>&lt;url&gt;</code></link> elements within the "
"application’s <code>&lt;component&gt;</code> in its metainfo file."
msgstr ""
"Odkazy pre aplikáciu sú uložené ako prvky <link href=\"https://www.freedesktop.org/software/"
"appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-url\"><code>&lt;url&gt;</code></link> v rámci "
"<code>&lt;component&gt;</code> aplikácie v jej súbore metainfo."

#. (itstool) path: section/p
#: C/software-metadata.page:322
msgid ""
"Add as many of the link types documented in the <link href=\"https://www.freedesktop.org/"
"software/appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-url\">appstream specification</link> as are "
"available for the application. If no suitable page exists for a given link type, it doesn’t have "
"to be included."
msgstr ""
"Pridajte toľko typov odkazov dokumentovaných v <link href=\"https://www.freedesktop.org/software/"
"appstream/docs/chap-Metadata.html#tag-url\">špecifikácii appstream</link>, koľko je pre "
"aplikáciu dostupných. Ak pre daný typ odkazu neexistuje vhodná stránka, nemusí byť zahrnutá."

